===еҮәжқҘдәӢ===
* {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|еӨ©жҷәеӨ©зҡҮ}} 11е№ҙ ({{ill|672 AD|ja|672е№ҙ}}) вҖ“ {{ill|Renjin Rebellion|ja|еЈ¬з”ігҒ®д№ұ}}.
* In {{ill|Meiji|ja|жҳҺжІ»}} 5 ({{ill|1872 AD|ja|1872е№ҙ}}), the family register compiled at that time was called the {{ill|Renjin Family Register|ja|еЈ¬з”іжҲёзұҚ}}.

==еЈ¬з”ігҒ®жңҲ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|з”І}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|е·ұ}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7жңҲ}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жңҲ (жҡҰ)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жңҲ}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зҜҖжңҲ}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|з«Ӣз§Ӣ}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|зҷҪйңІ}}) as applicable.

==еЈ¬з”ігҒ®ж—Ҙ==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ}} for {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}} is as follows.

===йҒёж—Ҙ===
The day of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hanto|ja|зҠҜеңҹ|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=еӨ§еңҹ}}.

==еЈ¬з”іжҷӮ==
It refers to the period from 16:00 to 18:00.


