* In {{ill|Meiji|ja|жҳҺжІ»}} 5 ({{ill|1872 AD|ja|1872е№ҙ}}), the family register compiled at that time was called the {{ill|Renjin Family Register|ja|еЈ¬з”іжҲёзұҚ}}.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|з”І|1=Kinoe (з”І)}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|е·ұ|1=Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7жңҲ}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жңҲ (жҡҰ)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жңҲ}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зҜҖжңҲ}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|з«Ӣз§Ӣ}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|зҷҪйңІ}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu}} for {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}} is as follows.

==={{nihongo|selection days|йҒёж—Ҙ|senjitsu}}===
The day of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hanto|ja|зҠҜеңҹ|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=еӨ§еңҹ}}.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”іжҷӮ==
It refers to the period from 16:00 to 18:00.


