'''еЈ¬з”і''' (mizu no esaru, jinsui no saru, jinshin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 9th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinwei|ja|иҫӣжңӘ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Guiyou|ja|зҷёй…ү|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|еЈ¬|1=Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|ж°ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёз”ҹпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒҳгӮҮгҒҶпјү|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=зӣёз”ҹ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (i.e. Metal generates Water).

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 12 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|е№ҙ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

