==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|з”І|1=Kinoe (з”І)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|е·ұ|1=Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7жңҲ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жңҲ (жҡҰ)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жңҲ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зҜҖжңҲ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|з«Ӣз§Ӣ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|зҷҪйңІ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} for {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is as follows.

