The day of {{ill|Renjin|ja|еЈ¬з”і|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hanto|ja|зҠҜеңҹ|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=еӨ§еңҹ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

