'''еЈ¬з”і''' (mizu no esaru, jinsui no saru, jinshin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 9th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinwei|ja|1=Yin Metal Goat|2=ja|иҫӣжңӘ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinwei|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Guiyou|ja|зҷёй…ү|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=зҷёй…ү|4=zh|5-зҷёй…ү|6=ko|7=кі„мң |lt_ko=кі„мң |8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guiyou|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|еЈ¬|1=Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|ж°ҙ|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (ж°ҙ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|еҚҒдәҢж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Monkey|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|йҮ‘|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (йҮ‘)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|дә”иЎҢжҖқжғі#зӣёз”ҹпјҲгҒқгҒҶгҒҳгӮҮгҒҶпјү|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=зӣёз”ҹ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (i.e. Metal generates Water).

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=иҘҝжҡҰ|4=zh|5=е…¬е…ғ|6=es|7=Era comГәn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} that leaves a remainder of 12 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|е№ҙ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/year|qq=}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|еЈ¬з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renjin|qq=}}.

