==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|иҘҝжҡҰ|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=иҘҝжҡҰ|4=zh|5=е…¬е…ғ|6=es|7=Era comГәn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 4 or 9 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|з”І|1=Kinoe (з”І)|lt=Kinoe (з”І)|2=ja|3=з”І|4=zh|5=з”І|1=Kinoe (з”І)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe (з”І)|qq=}} or {{ill|Ki|ja|е·ұ|1=Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)|lt=Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)|2=ja|3=е·ұ|4=zh|5=е·ұ|1=Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoto (е·ұ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7жңҲ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жңҲ (жҡҰ)|lt=Month|lt_ja=жңҲ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Renjin|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|еЈ¬з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renjin|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|ж—§жҡҰ|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|зҜҖжңҲ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|з«Ӣз§Ӣ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Beginning of Autumn|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|зҷҪйңІ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/White Dew|qq=}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”і)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|йҒёж—Ҙ|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for {{ill|Renjin|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|еЈ¬з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renjin|qq=}} is as follows.

==={{nihongo|selection days|йҒёж—Ҙ|senjitsu|qq=}}===
The day of {{ill|Renjin|ja|1=Yang Water Monkey|2=ja|еЈ¬з”і|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Renjin|qq=}} is the 3rd day of {{ill|Hanto|ja|зҠҜеңҹ|lt=Large Earth|lt_ja=еӨ§еңҹ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hanto|qq=}}.

==Yang Water Monkey (еЈ¬з”іжҷӮ==
It refers to the period from 16:00 to 18:00.

