'''еЈ¬з”і''' (mizu no esaru, jinsui no saru, jinshin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 9th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|е…ӯеҚҒе№Іж”Ҝ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinwei|ja|1=Yin Metal Goat|2=ja|иҫӣжңӘ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinwei|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinwei|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Metal Goat|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Guiyou|ja|зҷёй…ү|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=зҷёй…ү|4=zh|5-зҷёй…ү|6=ko|7=кі„мң |lt_ko=кі„мң |8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guiyou|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guiyou|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢжҖқжғі|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=йҷ°йҷҪдә”иЎҢ|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|еҚҒе№І|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|еЈ¬|1=Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|lt=Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|2=ja|3=еЈ¬|4=zh|5=еЈ¬|1=Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (еЈ¬)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Water|zh|Water (ж°ҙ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (ж°ҙ)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРҙР° (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FГјmf-ElemГӨnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thб»§y (NgЕ© hГ nh)|10=pt|11=ГҒgua (astrologia)|lt=Water (ж°ҙ)|2=uk|3=Р’РҫРҙР° (РЈ-СҒС–РҪ)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische FГјmf-ElemГӨnt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wu